          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is Baudie a deodorant?",
            "answer": "<p>No. Baudie is not a deodorant and does not replace one. It is a Deodorant Enhancer that works before deodorant to stop odor at the source and create the perfect base for your deo to shine.</p>"
